</html><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2F2F4F><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ukazarksnaketongue.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kazark Snaketongue</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>knows that Warriors are Superior</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>25</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>2/4/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>3:12:38 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Some high level insight needed</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Just realized something.  ROFLMAO we will see alot more dead rangers now when their offensive cap goes up.  Monks can FD and we can get back up on aggro list,  Rogues can evade, Hows a ranger going to lose aggro?  Hehe they'll die.  Man Verant is dumb but sucks to be rangers.  Oh yeah started my SK up again lol.  I can see Iksars being better tanks now.  Life taps will give them better HP then a warrior.  Also their AC will be better too.  Scales, Plus Velious armor.  Man Verant is stupid but oh well...<br>
<br>
Kazark Snaketongue, 53 Iksar Soldier<br>
 Member of Arcis on Povar</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ulyriel2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lyriel2</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>knows that Warriors are Superior</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>17</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>2/4/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>9:52:52 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B>&nbsp;<FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Some high level insight needed</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I've been thinking about this newest set of changes to the hybrid/warrior class balance.  If you plan to keep your warrior, play it exactly as Verant seems to want you to play it.  Warriors are meatshields and taunters, NOT IN ANY WAY, damage dealers.  Don't waste money on expensive weapons.  Just get a couple of fast, cheap taunting weapons like a pair of yaks.  Don't waste money on jade maces, lam's, etc.  Just taunt and get hit, that's all the warrior is for.  If you're in a group and win a roll on something expensive, like the jade mace....sell it.  Just keep any cobalt that happens to drop.  I think spending money on weapons has become unwise.  AC and ability to taunt, that's it.  </font><P><html>
